I think you misread my post, Logo...

::Striker::

Striker chuckles, frowning a bit as he sees Spears wince. "No, not the Ark, 
the Cybertronian Fire. We recently moved there from the Ark. The engines are 
shot there as well, but other than that, its fully fuctional."

He transforms into robot mode, looking at Spears. "Would it be easier for you 
if I carried you?"
